Summary:	Zigbee to MQTT bridge
Name:		zigbee2mqtt
Version:	2.6.0
Release:	1
License:	GPL v3+
Group:		Applications
Source0:	https://github.com/Koenkk/zigbee2mqtt/archive/%{version}/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	009f40c44fda4d047cf065a42c886373
